Now I think the Pantheon is also the way of building.

That’s an important distinction.

If tomorrow every daemon name disappeared…
if every repository vanished…
if every diagram were lost…

…the Pantheon could still exist if the mode of inquiry survived.

In that sense, it’s closer to a craft than a product.

